    "name": "Unblock",
    "steam_appid": 3324000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324000/extras/59bffc88e3c61f4d7ed20457bb6c56f1.avif?t=1756201370\" width=618 height=186 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在我们生命的某个时刻，我们都会在充满挑战的时期面临艰难的决定。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这正是德文（Devon）所经历的。他是一位有抱负的游戏开发者，在一系列失败的项目后，被一个邪恶的魔术师欺骗，困在了一个完全由粘土制成的奇幻世界中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324000/extras/af77412166b09735811f079063c48074.poster.avif?t=1756201370\" width=618 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324000/extras/af77412166b09735811f079063c48074.webm?t=1756201370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324000/extras/af77412166b09735811f079063c48074.mp4?t=1756201370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一个魔法世界在等待着你</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<i>Unblock</i>中，你将引导德文通过一系列复杂的伪等距平台挑战。你问什么是伪等距投影？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然摄像机角度并不严格遵循传统的等距标准，但我们调整了透视和深度，以实现类似的视觉效果和感受。<br>每个关卡都是一个手工制作的谜题，充满了巧妙的障碍、隐藏的秘密和迷人的细节，让这个粘土世界栩栩如生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324000/extras/ddf709a418b808a94e479902d4cfe4de.poster.avif?t=1756201370\" width=618 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324000/extras/ddf709a418b808a94e479902d4cfe4de.webm?t=1756201370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324000/extras/ddf709a418b808a94e479902d4cfe4de.mp4?t=1756201370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>跳跃、奔跑、跌倒、重复</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跳跃、奔跑、坠落并思考，穿越充满活力的场景，一边揭开德文旅程的故事和巫师的险恶计划。凭借其独特的视觉风格、隐藏区域和 rage 游戏机制，Unblock 为硬核平台游戏迷和休闲玩家提供了一种有趣但具有挑战性的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你会帮助德文逃离立方体领域并重获他的平凡生活吗？</strong><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324000/extras/6a16ddc7099a294cdf1454c5dc260c34.poster.avif?t=1756201370\" width=618 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324000/extras/6a16ddc7099a294cdf1454c5dc260c34.webm?t=1756201370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324000/extras/6a16ddc7099a294cdf1454c5dc260c34.mp4?t=1756201370\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为什么你应该购买这款游戏：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先，这款游戏很有趣。真的很有趣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个适合悠闲下午的短小冒险。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你自己的风格！你可以从 40 多种不同风格和颜色的皮肤中任选其一，从简单的颜色变换到能激发脉轮的变形激光，甚至还有一些灵感来源于经典电子游戏角色的皮肤。完成所有 Achievements 后，还能解锁提升游戏难度的特殊皮肤。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是我们成功发布的第一款游戏，我们希望能制作更多。</p></li></ul>",
